divs: Sighting DetailsThere was no sound, no trace of exhaust, no lights visible. It was just shortly after 2:00PM, when I was on my balcony and saw this ORB shaped object coming from the east side, and moving at a great speed to the Western direction. When I got a chance to grab my camera and turn it on, the object was almost out of sight, but I got this one photo of it anyways. I put the YELLOW highlighted circle around the object, so MAGNIFY that area to see the object.
Summary: Daytime sighting of ORB shaped object flying really fast through London, Ontario
